<Content>Great if you are flying into Schoenefeld I stayed here one night in June 2004 because it is so close to the airport. It was very cheap($95 USD) and very nice. They have a complimentary shuttle to pick you up at the aiport and take you back, no matter how early (we left at 5 am to catch another flight). The food in the restaurant is actually very good as well. We had a great salmon and pasta dish. I probably wouldn't recommend staying here if you are planning on seeing Berlin (we didn't have time), because it seems a bit far out from the city itself. But, great for aiport travelers just passing thru! 
